ActIndian Act
SubjectTransfer of lands in Douglas Lake Indian Reserve No. 3, British Columbia
PrecisOrder (1) consenting to the exercise of the power by the Province of British Columbia to take lands in DOUGLAS LAKE INDIAN RESERVE NO.3, British Columbia; and (2) authorizing, in lieu of such taking, the transfer of administration and control of the lands to the Province.
